interpretation: The "counterclockwise arrows button" card represents the need for change and a desire to go back to a previous state. It suggests that you may be feeling stuck or stagnant in your current situation and that it's time to shake things up. This card encourages you to revisit past experiences and learn from them, as well as to consider alternative approaches to your current challenges. It also highlights the importance of being flexible and adaptable in the face of change.
